{"about_the_game":"<strong>&quot;Land of Towers&quot;</strong> is a family-friendly VR adventure game that immerses the player in the amazing world of Medieval Caucasus. In this world, there's no need to rush: there's no room for commonplace battle scenes, but there is space for meditative exploration and creativity.<br><br><strong>Story</strong>: You will live the life of a humble watchtower keeper, finding joy in everyday work and minor adventures. The game equally combines a sense of duty with hope for something greater.<br><br><strong>Visual Design:</strong> The meticulously crafted mountain landscapes animate the game, creating unforgettable and realistic scenes.<br><br><strong>Physics and Interaction:</strong> Realistic physics and the ability to actively interact with objects in the world enrich the gameplay, making it lively and engaging.<br><br><strong>Realistic Tasks:</strong> You'll build ladders, craft tools, and engage in other lifelike activities, giving the game a unique charismatic touch.<br><br><strong>Sandbox Mode</strong>: Here your creativity knows no bounds. After completing the story, you can build and experiment, enjoying the freedom of choice.<br><br><strong>&quot;Land of Towers&quot;</strong> is not just a game; it's an art form that offers a fresh perspective on the VR genre. It is perfect for those looking for something fresh and unique, something more than just entertainment. This game is about adventure, craftsmanship, and the beauty of life.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"HIGHLANDER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2198970/f7f8490cac38af6e48379f9efd5d07e6219a31e1.jpg"},{"name":"WATCHMAN","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2198970/75c77511cb5211595c694fc1673aeceedf183871.jpg"},{"name":"PROSPECTOR'S CAMP","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2198970/66637b98a1df1826b276a3a6ae345cbcce54ddb1.jpg"},{"name":